  "article_text": "Welcome to the Star Atlas weekly recap from the Intergalactic Herald. Below is what happened with Star Atlas this past week.\nWe are looking for guests to be on our podcast. The podcast is a discussion of the past week’s news about Star Atlas. If you are interested in being on the podcast, please contact us.\nWe are launching a Star Atlas merch store. Please check it out at Intergalactic Gear.\nWe are creating a “non-guild” guild. If you are interested in learning more, please go to Intergalactic Coalition.\nIf you would like to support our efforts, donations can be sent to intergalacticherald.sol\nSolana’s Latency and Congestion Issues\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video talking about Solana’s congestion issues.\nSTAR ATLAS #228 Starbased – A SLOW Start!\nMetaVerse Explorer posted a video about Star Atlas updates.\nMetaverse Nomads #141 Star Atlas w/ BeyondTheHorizon\nMetaverse Nomads posted a video replay of their Star Atlas livestream.\nWEEKLY STAR ATLAS NEWSLETTER #124\nAephia published their weekly Star Atlas newsletter.\nStar Atlas Community – Learn Why Your Star Atlas Transactions Keep Failing\nSiggy tweeted a thread about Solana transactions failing.\nThe Atlas Brew #106\nStar Atlas TV posted a video of the latest Atlas Brew.\nPress Release: ECOS Holdings Acquires Superphoenix Titan\nHologram News Network published a press release about the acquisition of the Superphoenix Titan.\nStar Atlas Recap 4-10-24\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video of Star Atlas updates.\nStar Atlas Gameplay Walkthrough with CEO Michael Wagner\nDominicVain posted a video walkthrough of Star Atlas by CEO Michael Wagner.\nStar Atlas 101 — Starbased Day 1… A Preview of Crowded and Popular Game Loops\nGalia Crafters published an article about game loops in SAGE Starbased.\nStar Atlas SURGE EVENT Practice Tips\nBeyond the Horizon posted a video about tips for playing Star Atlas SURGE.",
